<caption><i>2nd-level evocation</i>
</caption><tbody><tr>
<th>Casting Time
</th><td>1 action
</td></tr>
<tr>
<th>Range
</th><td>60 feet
</td></tr>
<tr>
<th>Components
</th><td>V M (Bat fur, pitch/coal)
</td></tr>
<tr>
<th>Duration
</th><td>Conc. Up to 10 minutes
</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>Darkness spreads to fill a 15-foot-radius <a href="/wiki/Magic#Area_of_Effect" title="Magic">sphere</a> for the duration. The darkness goes around corners. A <a href="/wiki/Creature" title="Creature">creature</a> with darkvision can't see through this darkness, and nonmagical light can't illuminate it.
</p><p>If the point the darkness spreads from is an object you're holding or one that isn't being worn or carried, the darkness comes from and moves with the object. Completely covering the object with something opaque blocks the darkness.
</p><p>If this spell's area overlaps with light created by a 2nd-level spell or lower, the light and its spell ends.
</p>
